iv></div><div class="col-md-5" style="padding-bottom: 20px;"><img src="./img5_files/home-main.359935c39288e92d4dba5c9f2445b91d.svg" alt="home pic" class="img-fluid" style="max-height: 450px;"></div></div></div></div><div id="about" class="home-about-section container-fluid"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="home-about-description col-md-8"><h1 style="font-size: 2.6em;">LET ME <span class="purple"> INTRODUCE </span> MYSELF</h1><p class="home-about-body">I fell in love with programming and I have at least learnt something, I think… 🤷‍♂️<br><br>I am fluent in classics like<i><b class="purple"> C, Javascript and Java. </b></i><br><br>My field of Interest's are building new &nbsp;<i><b class="purple">Web Technologies and Products </b> and also in areas related to <b class="purple">CloudComputing.</b></i><br><br>Whenever possible, I also apply my passion for developing products with <b class="purple">Node.js</b> and<i><b class="purple"> Modern Javascript Library and Frameworks</b></i>&nbsp; like<i><b class="purple"> React.js and Next.js</b></i></p></div><div class="myAvtar col-md-4"><div style="will-change: transform; transition: 400ms cubic-bezier(0.03, 0.98, 0.52, 0.99); transform: perspective(1000px) rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg) scale3d(1, 1, 1);"><img src="./img5_files/avatar.7f806e40d46fc76fbc3c4a3d71349951.svg" class="img-fluid" alt="avatar"></div></div></div><div class="row"><div class="home-about-social col-md-12"><h1>FIND ME ON</h1><p>Feel free to <span class="purple">connect </span>with me</p><ul class="home-about-social-links"><li class="social-icons"><a href="https://github.com/Mathesh4193" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="icon-colour  home-social-icons"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M511.6 76.3C264.3 76.2 64 276.4 64 523.5 64 718.9 189.3 885 363.8 946c23.5 5.9 19.9-10.8 19.9-22.2v-77.5c-135.7 15.9-141.2-73.9-15